The '''Terkury Housing Complex''' was a building in [[Rellidir]], [[Tralus/Legends|Tralus]]. It was an upscale housing complex, created over a demolished site, and under construction as of the [[Battle of Tralus (Second Galactic Civil War)|Battle of Tralus]]. Its underground garage allowed [[Panther Flight]] a route under Rellidir's shield, allowing it to take down the rest of the shield for the other [[Corellian/Legends|Corellian]] forces to get through.

